{"tid":2478262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緬甸政變】軍方再通緝 20 演藝名人　女星：做正確的事感自豪","createTime":"2021-04-07T02:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:17:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"29e2eca77a183db39beceddf718a74a220018201","tid":2478262,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:24:10.000Z","msg":"緬甸政變發生超過兩個月，至今超過 570 名平民被軍方殺害。軍方在周日及周一（4、5 日）宣布，通緝 20 名一直支持示威的演藝名人，指控他們散播恐懼及假新聞。有被通緝的緬甸女星拍片回應，強調對自己做正確的事感到自豪，表明會繼續爭取公義民主。<br />\n<br />\n當地由軍方控制的報章《Global New Light of Myanmar》在周日、周一發布通緝名單，列出 20 人的相片、家鄉及 FB 專頁等。被通緝的包括多名支持反政變示威的演員、音樂人及社交媒體名人，他們將面臨最多 3 年的監禁。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方不斷打壓示威活動，並多次出手整頓聲援示威的演藝人士。早在今年 2 月政變發生初期，已經有多名演員被控。上周軍方控制的電視台亦發表了通緝名單。至今累計最少 60 人在通緝名單上。<br />\n<br />\n網上廣泛流傳一封相信是外洩的政府文件，警告廣播及製作公司不得發布這些藝人的作品，否則這些公司都會被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名被通緝的女演員 Myat Noe Aye 今日在 Twitter 發影片，形容自己是因為說真話已被通緝，「我以為我會很害怕，但我卻對自己為國家做正確的事感到很自豪」。她在片段中形容，軍方日間殺人、夜間搜捕異見，「不論他們如何困擾我們，我們都將繼續爭取公義民主」。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方持續血腥鎮壓示威，根據當地人權組織統計，至今最少 570 名示威者及旁觀者被殺害，包括 47 名兒童；另累計近 3,500 人被捕，當中五分四的人仍然被拘留。即使如此，人民仍然無懼打壓堅持上街。今日（6 日）仰光有示威者將紅色漆彈丟在馬路上，抗議軍方殺人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/緬甸政變-軍方再通緝-20-演藝名人-女星-做正確的事感自豪-繼續爭民主/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%86%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D-20-%E6%BC%94%E8%97%9D%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA-%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%9F-%E5%81%9A%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%84%9F%E8%87%AA%E8%B1%AA-%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E7%88%AD%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=da428ad4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%86%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D-20-%E6%BC%94%E8%97%9D%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA-%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%9F-%E5%81%9A%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%84%9F%E8%87%AA%E8%B1%AA-%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E7%88%AD%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%2F&h=5e6b3406\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/緬甸政變-軍方再通緝-20-演藝名人-女星-做正確的事感自豪-繼續爭民主/</a>"},{"pid":"46d5aa959238a322aea5f41039e2e05ac62f3a3c","tid":2478262,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223ad205394d778b4e32ddc9c409be2920a84a8b","tid":2478262,"uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tvb-24_WO9QB_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftvb-24_WO9QB_1200x0.png&h=be812e7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a1d0bc5dfe0a8555f8e4ca585f5e1c9d014ae8d","tid":2478262,"uid":40520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"香港個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d46bf185bee272d7ad0b21a2f16b27193cb74c","tid":2478262,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fafc2ff96b952225292d3a83616cc87ec01058","tid":2478262,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a1d0bc5dfe0a8555f8e4ca585f5e1c9d014ae8d","tid":2478262,"uid":40520,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"香港個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"香港明星 個個奶共搵食<br />\n仲有一班fans 幫佢地兜<br />\n<br />\n「明星 唔奶共就會失業, 到時你養